  "prompt": "Why can't I see views on my Instagram videos?",
  "response": "If you can't see views on your Instagram videos, there could be several reasons for this. Here are some common issues and solutions:\n\n### 1. **Account Type**\n   - **Personal Account:** Instagram only shows video views on **business accounts**, **creator accounts**, or **professional accounts**. If you have a **personal account**, you won\u2019t see views.\n   - **Solution:** Switch to a business or creator account. Go to **Settings > Account > Switch to Professional Account**.\n\n### 2. **Video Format**\n   - **Instagram Stories:** Views on Instagram Stories are displayed as the number of people who have seen your story, not as \"views.\"\n   - **Reels:** Video views are available for Reels, but they may take some time to update.\n   - **Solution:** Ensure you're checking the correct section (e.g., Reels, IGTV, or regular feed videos).\n\n### 3. **Video Privacy Settings**\n   - If your video is set to **private**, it won\u2019t accumulate views because only your approved followers can see it.\n   - **Solution:** Change the video\u2019s privacy settings to **public** if you want views to be counted.\n\n### 4. **App Glitch or Outdated Version**\n   - Sometimes, the Instagram app may have a bug or glitch that prevents views from showing up.\n   - **Solution:** Update the app to the latest version or try logging out and back in. If the issue persists, reinstall the app.\n\n### 5. **Delayed View Count**\n   - Instagram may take some time to update the view count, especially if the video was just posted.\n   - **Solution:** Wait a few minutes or hours and check again.\n\n### 6. **Technical Issues**\n   - Instagram\u2019s servers may be experiencing temporary issues.\n   - **Solution:** Check Instagram\u2019s status on platforms like [Downdetector](https://downdetector.com) or wait for the issue to resolve.\n\n### 7. **Video Length**\n   - Instagram only counts views for videos that are **3 seconds** or longer. Shorter videos may not register views.\n   - **Solution:** Ensure your video meets the minimum length requirement.\n\nIf none of these solutions work, consider reaching out to Instagram support for further assistance.",
